org.cpsolver.coursett

Class TimetableSolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.solver.Solver<Lecture,Placement>
      • org.cpsolver.coursett.TimetableSolver
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class TimetableSolver
extends Solver<Lecture,Placement>
    University course timetabling solver.

    When a complete solution is found, it is improved by limited depth backtracking search. This way it is ensured that the fund solution is at least locally optimal.

    Deprecated: use FixCompleteSolutionNeighbourSelection instead.
    Version:
    CourseTT 1.3 (University Course Timetabling)
